### AirServe Pro — API Test File
### Use with the "REST Client" VS Code extension (humao.rest-client)
### Set @token below after logging in

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@token = PASTE_YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ── AUTH ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Register new customer
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "full_name": "Test User",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "testpass123",
  "phone": "0912-000-0001",
  "address": "Test Street, QC"
}

###

### Login as admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@demo.com",
  "password": "demo1234"
}

###

### Login as customer
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "customer@demo.com",
  "password": "demo1234"
}

###

### Login as technician
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "tech@demo.com",
  "password": "demo1234"
}

###

### Get current user
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ── SERVICES ───────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get all services
GET {{baseUrl}}/services

###

### Create service (admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/services
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Deep Cleaning",
  "description": "Full disassembly deep cleaning service",
  "base_price": 750,
  "duration_hours": 2.5
}

###

### ── BOOKINGS ───────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create booking (customer)
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "service_id": 3,
  "scheduled_date": "2026-05-01",
  "scheduled_time": "09:00",
  "address": "123 Rizal Street, QC",
  "diagnostic": {
    "ac_type": "split",
    "problem": "Not cooling",
    "years_owned": "1-3 years",
    "location_type": "residential",
    "previously_repaired": false,
    "notes": "AC cools but not as cold as before"
  }
}

###

### Get all bookings
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get booking by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Update booking status (admin)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/bookings/1/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "confirmed",
  "technician_id": 3,
  "notes": "Confirmed and assigned to Rico"
}

###

### ── SCHEDULES ──────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get available time slots for a date
GET {{baseUrl}}/schedules?date=2026-05-01

###

### ── PAYMENTS ───────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create GCash payment
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/gcash/create
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "booking_id": 1,
  "amount": 700
}

###

### Create card payment
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments/card/create
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "booking_id": 1,
  "amount": 700,
  "billing": {
    "name": "Jane Dela Cruz",
    "email": "jane@email.com",
    "phone": "09123456789",
    "address": {
      "line1": "123 Rizal Street",
      "city": "Quezon City",
      "state": "NCR",
      "postal_code": "1100",
      "country": "PH"
    }
  },
  "card": {
    "number": "4343434343434345",
    "exp_month": 12,
    "exp_year": 2030,
    "cvc": "123"
  }
}

###

### Get payment by booking ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/payments/booking/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get all payments (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/payments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ── PRODUCTS ───────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get all products
GET {{baseUrl}}/products

###

### Create product (admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Thermostat Digital",
  "description": "Programmable digital thermostat",
  "sku": "THERM-DIG-001",
  "category": "Parts",
  "price": 850,
  "stock_quantity": 15,
  "low_stock_threshold": 3
}

###

### Restock product (admin)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/products/1/stock
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "quantity": 10,
  "operation": "add"
}

###

### ── ORDERS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Place order (customer)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    { "product_id": 7, "quantity": 2 },
    { "product_id": 10, "quantity": 1 }
  ]
}

###

### Get my orders
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ── USERS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get all users (admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get technicians
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/technicians
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Update user profile
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/2
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "full_name": "Jane Dela Cruz Updated",
  "phone": "0912-999-9999",
  "address": "456 New Street, QC"
}

###

### ── REPORTS ────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Admin dashboard stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Payment report with date filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/reports/payments?from=2026-01-01&to=2026-12-31
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ── NOTIFICATIONS ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get my notifications
GET {{baseUrl}}/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Mark all as read
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/notifications/read-all
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
